2026-03-29T16:02:33.2647606Z               "message": "Refactor build logs from per-build branches to single orphan branch\n\nStore all build logs as folders on a single `build-logs` orphan branch\ninstead of creating a separate orphan branch per build. Each build becomes\na folder named `<run>-<id>-<timestamp>-<status>`. Old folders are pruned\nto keep only the 10 most recent.\n\nThe GitHub Action uses `--filter=blob:none` to avoid downloading existing\nlog content when adding new builds. The skill uses blobless fetches with\n`-c` config overrides to read only the specific files needed without\npolluting the user's repo config.\n\nConcurrent build races are handled by a retry loop (up to 3 attempts\nwith backoff) that re-fetches and re-applies on push failure.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01YcBBPy1V3viff4r3qBtUgA",
