2026-03-29T16:02:33.2658995Z               "message": "Fix build-logs push: delete old-format branches and fix retry logic\n\nTwo issues caused the push-build-logs step to fail:\n\n1. Namespace conflict: Git refs can't be both a leaf and a directory,\n   so refs/heads/build-logs can't coexist with refs/heads/build-logs/296-*.\n   Fix: delete all old-format build-logs/* branches via GitHub API before\n   attempting to push.\n\n2. Retry bug: after a failed push, git rm --cached cleared the index but\n   HEAD still pointed to the committed tree, so re-adding the folder made\n   the index match HEAD again (\"nothing to commit\"). Fix: reset to orphan\n   state at the start of each retry attempt.\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01YcBBPy1V3viff4r3qBtUgA",
